 "remarks": "Welcome to Midtown Estates! Best location in the complex with natural light on three sides. Enjoy all that vibrant downtown Stamford has to offer! This stylish townhome offers excellent plenty of space and convenience and features hardwood floors, recessed lighting and detailed millwork. The entry foyer with built-ins leads to a sun-filled main level featuring an open floor plan with living room, dining area and sliders to a private balcony. The designer kitchen showcases the Carrara Marble countertops, breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. A powder room completes this level. Upstairs, you&apos;ll find two generous bedrooms and a hall bath with both a tub and separate shower. The third level is dedicated to the primary bedroom with a walk-in closet featuring custom built-ins and a full bath. But wait, there&apos;s more! A private rooftop deck with fabulous views is perfect for relaxing or entertaining. There is ample street parking to compliment the attached 2 car garage with custom storage.",
